{"id":335061,"type":6,"name":"ソロモンの偽証","summary":"クリスマスの朝、雪の積もった校庭で藤野涼子（上白石萌歌）はクラスメイト・柏木卓也の死体を発見する。警察や高校が自殺と断定する中、涼子のもとに“同級生・大出俊次らによる殺人“を告発する匿名の手紙が届く。自殺か他殺か、転落死をめぐって騒ぎ出すマスコミやSNS。校長の津崎正男は事態の収束をはかるも、更なる事故が起きてしまう。次々に起こる不可解な出来事。大人たちの対応に納得できない涼子は謎の他校生・神原和彦とともに立ち上がる。「裁判をしませんか。わたしたちで」前代未聞の学校内裁判が始まる――。","info":"<li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/19920\">宮部みゆき</a>『ソロモンの偽証』（新潮文庫刊）</li><li><span>编剧: </span><a href=\"/person/22773\">篠﨑絵里子</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/3199\">羽岡佳</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/32989\">上白石萌歌</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>8</li><li><span>开始: </span>2021年秋</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日本语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>WOWOW</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://www.wowow.co.jp/drama/original/solomon/</li><li><span>导演: </span>権野元</li>","eps":[{"id":1028124,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028124","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028125,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028125","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028126,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028126","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028127,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028127","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028128,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028128","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028129,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028129","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028130,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028130","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1028131,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1028131","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","